<div id="second_layer">
  <div id="introduction">
    <h2>Become a super developer!</h2>

    <h3>Mash your web presence into a single profile page. Share your blog, tweets, github updates and much more with
      other devs.</h3>

    <div id="introduction_links">
      <a id="join_us_link" href="<%= register_path %>">Join us!</a> or <a id="see_users" href="<%= users_path %>">See who's already in</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="third_layer">
  <div id="key_points">
    <div style="float:left;">
      <h4>Share</h4>

      <p>Combine your accounts that define your development identity. With one link you can share your latest tweets, contact details, blog entries, and git commits with other developers.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="float:left;">
      <h4>Learn</h4>

      <p>Check out the latest trends in the development community. Find out what popular developers are interested in or read blogs of developers with interests similar to yours.  </p>
    </div>
    <div style="float:left;">
      <h4>Socialise</h4>

      <p>Meet other developers at conferences or user groups near you. Stay up to date with events related to your interests. Follow other developers and gain popularity within the community.</p>

    </div>
    <div style="clear:both;"></div>
  </div>
</div>

